WEBVTT

00:02.252 --> 00:04.296
[ Horn blares ]

00:14.765 --> 00:16.057
Man on radio:  THE FIRST PRIORITY

00:14.765 --> 00:16.057
FOR NEW ENGLAND

00:16.099 --> 00:18.059
IS TO GET THEIR DEFENSE

00:16.099 --> 00:18.059
HEALTHY.

00:18.101 --> 00:19.561
THEIR DEFENSE IS FINE,

00:18.101 --> 00:19.561
YOU MORONS.

00:19.603 --> 00:21.939
THEY ALLOWED AN AVERAGE

00:19.603 --> 00:21.939
OF 10 POINTS PER GAME LAST YEAR.

00:21.981 --> 00:23.273
...THROW FOR, YOU KNOW --

00:23.315 --> 00:24.650
HE WAS, WHAT,

00:23.315 --> 00:24.650
I THINK HE WAS 7 OF...

00:28.445 --> 00:29.404
[ GUN COCKS ]

00:31.949 --> 00:32.992
[ GUN COCKS ]

00:34.535 --> 00:35.828
[ GUNFIRE, SCREAMING ]

00:35.870 --> 00:37.788
[ Russian accent ]

00:35.870 --> 00:37.788
EVERYBODY DOWN! DOWN!

00:39.540 --> 00:40.374
HELL!

00:43.669 --> 00:45.379
NO! NO!

00:50.133 --> 00:51.259
GET AWAY FROM THE VEHICLE!

00:51.301 --> 00:53.387
[ GUNSHOTS, MAN GRUNTS ]

00:54.304 --> 00:57.349
Man:  DAVAI! DAVAI!

00:54.304 --> 00:57.349
DAVAI! DAVAI! DAVAI!

01:00.895 --> 01:03.480
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

01:04.899 --> 01:08.193
I'VE BEEN A COP WITH THE BOSTON

01:04.899 --> 01:08.193
P.D. FOR OVER 20 YEARS.

01:08.235 --> 01:09.611
MY WIFE GOT LAID OFF

01:08.235 --> 01:09.611
A COUPLE MONTHS AGO,

01:09.653 --> 01:11.822
SO I PICKED UP SOME SHIFTS

01:09.653 --> 01:11.822
WITH A SECURITY COMPANY

01:11.864 --> 01:13.365
TO MAKE ENDS MEET.

01:13.407 --> 01:17.327
MR. COSPITO, YOU WERE DOING

01:13.407 --> 01:17.327
A SIDE JOB FOR KERRITY DIAMONDS?

01:17.369 --> 01:19.454
PLEASE, CALL ME JOEY.

01:19.496 --> 01:22.666
I'M FEELING LIKE AN OLD MAN

01:19.496 --> 01:22.666
THESE DAYS AS IT IS.

01:22.708 --> 01:25.002
I WAS HAULING ABOUT $10 MILLION

01:22.708 --> 01:25.002
IN DIAMONDS THAT DAY.

01:25.044 --> 01:27.421
I'D DONE THE SAME ROUTE FIVE,

01:25.044 --> 01:27.421
MAYBE SIX TIMES BEFORE --

01:27.462 --> 01:29.006
NO PROBLEM.

01:29.048 --> 01:31.050
ARMORED-CAR DRIVERS ARE SUPPOSED

01:29.048 --> 01:31.050
TO STAY WITH THE VEHICLE, RIGHT?

01:31.090 --> 01:32.384
I'M A COP FIRST.

01:32.426 --> 01:35.679
MY INSTINCT WAS

01:32.426 --> 01:35.679
STOP A ROBBERY IN PROGRESS.

01:35.721 --> 01:38.181
HELL OF A JOB I DID, HUH?

01:38.223 --> 01:41.769
ONE GUARD

01:38.223 --> 01:41.769
FOR A DELIVERY THAT SIZE?

01:41.810 --> 01:43.020
AH, THESE DAYS,

01:43.062 --> 01:45.272
WITH COMPANIES PINCHING

01:43.062 --> 01:45.272
ANYWHERE THEY CAN,

01:45.313 --> 01:46.481
HAPPENS ALL THE TIME.

01:46.523 --> 01:48.567
IT SOUNDS TO ME

01:46.523 --> 01:48.567
LIKE AN INSIDE JOB.

01:48.609 --> 01:51.111
EXCEPT THEY THOUGHT

01:48.609 --> 01:51.111
THE INSIDE MAN WAS ME.

01:51.152 --> 01:52.905
HEY, I KNOW --

01:51.152 --> 01:52.905
FIRST GUY YOU LOOK AT

01:52.947 --> 01:55.198
IS THE BLUE-COLLAR GUY

01:52.947 --> 01:55.198
WHO'S GOT MONEY TROUBLE.

01:55.240 --> 01:58.577
UNTIL THIS INVESTIGATION'S

01:55.240 --> 01:58.577
CLOSED AND MY NAME IS CLEARED,

01:58.619 --> 02:01.121
I'M SUSPENDED FROM THE FORCE

01:58.619 --> 02:01.121
WITHOUT PAY.

02:01.162 --> 02:03.707
YEAH, ALTHOUGH,

02:01.162 --> 02:03.707
NOT MUCH OF AN INVESTIGATION.

02:03.749 --> 02:06.167
NO WITNESSES, NO PRINTS.

02:06.209 --> 02:08.253
TRACE ELEMENTS

02:06.209 --> 02:08.253
OF THE EXPLOSIVE THEY USED,

02:08.295 --> 02:09.296
FAST-BURNING DET CORD.

02:09.337 --> 02:12.466
MEDICAL BILLS ARE PILING UP.

02:12.507 --> 02:13.759
AND THERE'S NO WORK

02:12.507 --> 02:13.759
FOR A GUY

02:13.801 --> 02:15.636
WITH A BUM SHOULDER

02:13.801 --> 02:15.636
AND AN OPEN INVESTIGATION.

02:15.677 --> 02:17.554
ALL RIGHT, LISTEN, JOEY,

02:15.677 --> 02:17.554
WE'RE GONNA DO EVERYTHING WE CAN

02:17.596 --> 02:18.931
TO HELP YOU WITH THAT,

02:17.596 --> 02:18.931
ALL RIGHT?

02:18.973 --> 02:21.266
NEVER THOUGHT IT'D BE SO TOUGH

02:21.308 --> 02:25.062
JUST TO TRY AND KEEP A ROOF

02:21.308 --> 02:25.062
OVER MY FAMILY'S HEAD, YOU KNOW?

02:25.104 --> 02:26.647
YEAH.

02:26.688 --> 02:27.773
[ SIGHS ]

02:27.815 --> 02:29.483
WHO'S THE OTHER DRINK FOR?

02:30.651 --> 02:31.944
THE, UH...

02:31.986 --> 02:33.403
OH, SHE'S, UH...

02:36.824 --> 02:37.825
NOBODY.

02:39.952 --> 02:43.246
THE RICH AND POWERFUL,

02:39.952 --> 02:43.246
THEY TAKE WHAT THEY WANT.

02:43.288 --> 02:45.540
WE STEAL IT BACK FOR YOU.

02:48.961 --> 02:52.923
AND SOMETIMES, BAD GUYS

02:48.961 --> 02:52.923
MAKE THE BEST GOOD GUYS.

02:54.716 --> 02:57.302
WE PROVIDE...

03:02.057 --> 03:04.518
JIM KERRITY III --

03:02.057 --> 03:04.518
HE TOOK OVER KERRITY DIAMONDS

03:04.559 --> 03:07.104
FOUR YEARS AGO,

03:04.559 --> 03:07.104
AFTER HIS OLD MAN RETIRED.

03:07.146 --> 03:08.563
AND IN THAT SMALL AMOUNT

03:07.146 --> 03:08.563
OF TIME,

03:08.605 --> 03:10.899
HE MANAGED TO DRIVE THE BUSINESS

03:08.605 --> 03:10.899
STRAIGHT INTO THE GROUND

03:10.941 --> 03:12.151
BY LIVING WAY BEYOND HIS MEANS.

03:12.191 --> 03:14.987
I'M TALKING DRUGS, BOOZE, WOMEN.

03:15.029 --> 03:17.156
ACCORDING TO HIS CREDIT CARDS,

03:15.029 --> 03:17.156
SAME AS -- WHAT?

03:17.196 --> 03:18.991
WHAT? WHAT? WHY? WHAT?

03:17.196 --> 03:18.991
WHAT ARE YOU DOING? WHAT? WHAT?

03:19.033 --> 03:20.951
-WHAT?

03:19.033 --> 03:20.951
-IT'S DISTRACTING.

03:20.993 --> 03:22.452
WELL, THE COUCH IS JUST FEELING

03:20.993 --> 03:22.452
A LITTLE EMPTY.

03:22.494 --> 03:24.746
ELIOT, WILL YOU PLEASE

03:22.494 --> 03:24.746
SIT NEXT TO PARKER?

03:24.788 --> 03:26.456
NO.

03:24.788 --> 03:26.456
I'M SITTING HERE NOW.

03:26.498 --> 03:29.001
GUYS, GUYS, ALL RIGHT,

03:26.498 --> 03:29.001
WE ALL MISS SOPHIE.

03:29.043 --> 03:30.335
WE JUST HAVE TO ADAPT.

03:30.377 --> 03:32.671
-I GOT THIS. MOVE. GO. BYE.

03:30.377 --> 03:32.671
-PLEASE.

03:32.713 --> 03:34.798
GO.

03:34.840 --> 03:36.216
YOU HAPPY?

03:37.676 --> 03:40.137
NOW, KERRITY'S FINANCES

03:37.676 --> 03:40.137
ARE A MESS --

03:40.179 --> 03:43.223
MAXED OUT, MAXED OUT, OVERDRAWN.

03:43.264 --> 03:45.184
ACCORDING TO

03:43.264 --> 03:45.184
THE INSURANCE CLAIM,

03:45.225 --> 03:47.352
HE STANDS TO GAIN $9 MILLION

03:45.225 --> 03:47.352
FROM THE ARMORED-CAR ROBBERY.

03:47.394 --> 03:50.022
YOU KNOW, A GUY LIKE THIS,

03:47.394 --> 03:50.022
HE GETS IN OVER HIS HEAD,

03:50.064 --> 03:52.191
AND HIS INSURANCE POLICY STARTS

03:50.064 --> 03:52.191
TO LOOK PRETTY ATTRACTIVE.

03:52.232 --> 03:54.359
HIRES A COUPLE OF THUGS,

03:52.232 --> 03:54.359
KNOCKS OFF HIS OWN TRUCK.

03:54.401 --> 03:55.944
IT'S A SWEET PAYOUT, TOO.

03:55.986 --> 03:58.613
HE GETS THE INSURANCE CLAIM,

03:55.986 --> 03:58.613
PLUS HE STILL HAS THE DIAMONDS.

03:58.655 --> 04:01.075
MM-HMM, AND HONEST PEOPLE

03:58.655 --> 04:01.075
LIKE JOEY TAKE THE HEAT.

04:01.116 --> 04:03.160
YOU KNOW, THE THING ABOUT THIS

04:01.116 --> 04:03.160
MOST PEOPLE DON'T UNDERSTAND

04:03.202 --> 04:04.912
IS INSURANCE FRAUD --

04:03.202 --> 04:04.912
IT'S A LOT OF RED TAPE.

04:04.953 --> 04:06.621
I MEAN, A BIG CLAIM LIKE THIS --

04:06.663 --> 04:09.457
IT'LL TAKE ABOUT A YEAR BEFORE

04:06.663 --> 04:09.457
KERRITY SEES ANY OF THE MONEY.

04:09.499 --> 04:11.501
AND THE BILL COLLECTORS --

04:09.499 --> 04:11.501
THEY'RE NOT GONNA WAIT AROUND.

04:11.543 --> 04:13.795
-HE'S GOT TO FENCE THE DIAMONDS.

04:11.543 --> 04:13.795
-HE CAN'T.

04:13.837 --> 04:16.173
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

04:13.837 --> 04:16.173
-HIS DIAMONDS ARE GIA-CERTIFIED,

04:16.215 --> 04:18.842
VVS CLARITY,

04:16.215 --> 04:18.842
ALL ABOUT TWO CARATS.

04:18.884 --> 04:19.968
THAT'S MY CLICKER.

04:20.010 --> 04:21.595
WHO STOLE THE POLAR STAR?

04:21.636 --> 04:23.513
WHO STOLE THE GEM OF GIBRALTAR?

04:23.555 --> 04:25.515
DAMIANI RAID?

04:23.555 --> 04:25.515
ME.

04:25.557 --> 04:26.934
I KNOW DIAMONDS.

04:26.975 --> 04:30.353
AND OUR BAD GUY

04:26.975 --> 04:30.353
CAN'T FENCE THOSE DIAMONDS

04:30.395 --> 04:31.855
BECAUSE STONES THAT SIZE

04:31.897 --> 04:34.649
HAVE AN I.D. NUMBER

04:31.897 --> 04:34.649
LASER-INSCRIBED ON THEM.

04:34.691 --> 04:35.943
OH, SO IT'S LIKE A STOLEN CAR.

04:35.984 --> 04:37.485
YOU GOT TO CLEAN THE VIN

04:35.984 --> 04:37.485
BEFORE YOU CAN SELL THEM.

04:37.527 --> 04:39.571
HOW DO YOU GET

04:37.527 --> 04:39.571
THAT I.D. NUMBER OFF?

04:39.613 --> 04:43.200
WITH A SPECIAL LASER,

04:39.613 --> 04:43.200
BUT ONLY THREE GUYS CAN DO IT --

04:43.242 --> 04:45.911
ANTWERP, DUBAI, TEL AVIV.

04:45.953 --> 04:51.083
AND AS OF RIGHT NOW,

04:45.953 --> 04:51.083
BOSTON, RIGHT?

04:51.125 --> 04:52.918
I MEAN, KERRITY

04:51.125 --> 04:52.918
HAS TO MOVE HIS DIAMONDS,

04:52.960 --> 04:54.920
SO WE CONVINCE HIM

04:52.960 --> 04:54.920
THAT WE'RE THE ONLY PEOPLE

04:54.962 --> 04:56.713
WHO CAN MAKE THEM CLEAN ENOUGH

04:54.962 --> 04:56.713
TO MOVE.

04:56.755 --> 04:58.257
GET THEM TO BRING THE DIAMONDS

04:56.755 --> 04:58.257
TO US.

04:58.298 --> 04:59.591
AND WHEN HE SHOWS UP --

04:59.633 --> 05:01.593
OH, HARDISON, CAN YOU PUT

04:59.633 --> 05:01.593
THE CRIME-SCENE PHOTOS...

05:01.635 --> 05:04.138
CAN -- CAN...

05:04.179 --> 05:07.141
STATE POLICE GUY,

05:04.179 --> 05:07.141
LIEUTENANT BONANNO.

05:07.182 --> 05:10.685
YEAH. SO, WE DROP KERRITY ON HIS

05:07.182 --> 05:10.685
LAP WITH THE STOLEN DIAMONDS.

05:10.727 --> 05:12.938
LIEUTENANT BONANNO DROPS

05:10.727 --> 05:12.938
THE HAMMER.

05:12.980 --> 05:14.982
OUR GUY GETS CLEARED,

05:12.980 --> 05:14.982
GETS HIS JOB BACK.

05:15.023 --> 05:17.525
PARDON ME, BUT I DON'T MEAN

05:15.023 --> 05:17.525
TO STOP THE FUN TRAIN --

05:17.567 --> 05:18.735
WE'RE OUT A GRIFTER HERE.

05:18.777 --> 05:20.070
I KNOW WHO WE CAN CALL.

05:20.112 --> 05:21.738
NO.

05:20.112 --> 05:21.738
WE'RE NOT GONNA CALL SOPHIE.

05:21.780 --> 05:23.657
NO. SHE HAS ASKED FOR SPACE,

05:21.780 --> 05:23.657
AND WE'RE GONNA HONOR THAT.

05:23.698 --> 05:24.741
NO.

05:24.783 --> 05:26.785
HARDISON,

05:24.783 --> 05:26.785
YOU'RE GONNA BE OUR GRIFTER.

05:26.827 --> 05:28.662
-I'M LISTENING.

05:26.827 --> 05:28.662
-WHAT? NO, NO, NO.

05:28.703 --> 05:30.330
-PARKER, YOU'LL BE THE ROPER.

05:28.703 --> 05:30.330
-WHAT?

05:30.371 --> 05:32.082
CUTE DRESS, HEELS --

05:30.371 --> 05:32.082
YOU'LL BE FINE.

05:32.124 --> 05:34.042
SURE.

05:32.124 --> 05:34.042
I'LL BE FINE.

05:34.084 --> 05:36.003
ELIOT, YOU BE THE MUSCLE.

05:37.129 --> 05:38.421
HI.

05:38.463 --> 05:39.506
HELLO.

05:39.547 --> 05:40.799
BUY ME A DRINK?

05:40.841 --> 05:42.341
YOU GOT IT.

05:44.511 --> 05:46.387
SO...

05:47.639 --> 05:49.183
AAH!

05:49.224 --> 05:50.475
[ GRUNTS ]

05:50.517 --> 05:52.144
AAH!

05:52.186 --> 05:54.021
Nate:

05:52.186 --> 05:54.021
PARKER? PARKER?

05:54.062 --> 05:57.107
[ MAN SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

05:57.149 --> 05:58.817
AAH!

05:58.859 --> 06:01.278
[ CROWD GASPING, MURMURING ]

06:02.988 --> 06:05.657
YEAH.

06:02.988 --> 06:05.657
I'LL BE FINE.

06:05.699 --> 06:08.827
I WILL NOT BE FINE.

06:05.699 --> 06:08.827
I STABBED THAT GUY WITH A FORK!

06:08.869 --> 06:10.453
PARKER, PARKER, RELAX.

06:08.869 --> 06:10.453
IT'S FINE.

06:10.495 --> 06:12.206
LISTEN, GO TO NATE'S

06:10.495 --> 06:12.206
STORAGE CUPBOARD,

06:12.247 --> 06:14.041
AND YOU'RE GONNA FIND

06:12.247 --> 06:14.041
A SEXY LITTLE MINIDRESS

06:14.082 --> 06:15.667
AND MY EMERGENCY JIMMY CHOOS.

06:15.709 --> 06:16.710
JIMMY WHO?

06:16.751 --> 06:18.503
YOU HAVE A BODY

06:16.751 --> 06:18.503
IN NATE'S CLOSET?

06:18.545 --> 06:19.880
SHOES, PARKER!

06:19.921 --> 06:22.507
DIDN'T I TEACH YOU ANY--

06:19.921 --> 06:22.507
ALL RIGHT, LISTEN.

06:22.549 --> 06:24.051
Okay, this is the important bit.

06:24.092 --> 06:25.844
DO YOU STILL HAVE THE ROSALIND

06:24.092 --> 06:25.844
DIAMOND YOU STOLE IN PERTH?

06:25.886 --> 06:26.845
YES.

06:26.887 --> 06:28.471
WEAR IT.

06:28.513 --> 06:31.058
THE DIAMOND WILL SPEAK FOR YOU.

06:28.513 --> 06:31.058
YOU WON'T HAVE TO SAY A WORD.

06:31.099 --> 06:34.519
This is the key to the grift.

06:31.099 --> 06:34.519
You just trust the character.

06:34.561 --> 06:37.438
SAY NOTHING.

06:34.561 --> 06:37.438
TRUST THE DIAMOND.

06:37.480 --> 06:40.025
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

06:37.480 --> 06:40.025
I CAN DO THAT.

06:40.067 --> 06:42.027
DON'T TELL NATE I CALLED.

06:42.069 --> 06:43.862
I WON'T.

06:43.904 --> 06:44.738
[ BEEPS ]

06:45.739 --> 06:47.574
[ BEEPS ]

06:47.615 --> 06:50.160
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYS ]

07:11.265 --> 07:12.933
WHERE'S THE MARK?

07:15.310 --> 07:19.022
KERRITY'S AT THE BAR --

07:15.310 --> 07:19.022
GOLD ROLEX, PURPLE TIE.

07:28.782 --> 07:31.534
SAY NOTHING.

07:28.782 --> 07:31.534
TRUST THE DIAMOND.

07:32.994 --> 07:35.956
SAY NOTHING

07:32.994 --> 07:35.956
AND TRUST THE DIAMOND.

07:35.997 --> 07:38.083
Parker, what are you saying?

07:38.125 --> 07:40.585
NOTHING.

07:38.125 --> 07:40.585
AND TRUSTING THE DIAMOND.

07:44.547 --> 07:46.591
I'LL HAVE AN APPLETINI.

07:46.633 --> 07:50.262
-THEY MAKE THEM STRONG HERE.

07:46.633 --> 07:50.262
-OH, DO THEY?

07:52.847 --> 07:55.642
IS THAT AN AUSTRALIAN

07:52.847 --> 07:55.642
PINK DIAMOND?

07:55.683 --> 07:58.979
IS THAT THE ROSALIND?

07:55.683 --> 07:58.979
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

07:59.020 --> 08:01.982
THAT'S AN IMPRESSIVE,

07:59.020 --> 08:01.982
UH, REPLICA.

08:02.023 --> 08:03.608
IT'S THE ORIGINAL.

08:07.028 --> 08:08.696
I'LL HAVE TO TAKE YOUR WORD

08:07.028 --> 08:08.696
FOR IT.

08:08.738 --> 08:10.907
I HAVE PEOPLE WHO CERTIFY

08:08.738 --> 08:10.907
THESE THINGS FOR ME.

08:10.949 --> 08:12.826
NATE: "Do you want

08:10.949 --> 08:12.826
to take a closer..."

08:12.867 --> 08:14.077
YOU WANT A CLOSER LOOK?

08:20.875 --> 08:23.170
No stabbing, Parker.

08:23.211 --> 08:25.297
Kerrity:

08:23.211 --> 08:25.297
THIS IS A VERY FAMOUS DIAMOND.

08:25.339 --> 08:26.381
HOW DID YOU GET IT?

08:26.423 --> 08:28.258
IT WAS A GIFT

08:26.423 --> 08:28.258
FROM MY BOYFRIEND.

08:28.300 --> 08:30.260
AH.

08:30.302 --> 08:32.179
HE WORKS IN DIAMONDS.

08:34.014 --> 08:37.017
SO DO I, AND I WOULD

08:34.014 --> 08:37.017
LOVE TO TALK SHOP

08:37.058 --> 08:39.811
WITH THE MAN WHO MANAGED

08:37.058 --> 08:39.811
TO GET HIS HANDS ON THE, UH...

08:39.853 --> 08:41.855
THE ROSALIND DIAMOND.

08:54.159 --> 08:56.370
[ British accent ] NO.

08:54.159 --> 08:56.370
N--

08:56.411 --> 08:57.829
COME HERE.

08:56.411 --> 08:57.829
WHAT HAVE I SAID?

08:57.871 --> 08:59.539
WHAT HAVE I SAID

08:57.871 --> 08:59.539
ABOUT NEW PEOPLE? HUH?

08:59.580 --> 09:00.623
WHAT HAVE I SAID?

09:02.042 --> 09:04.127
HEY, IT'S OKAY.

09:02.042 --> 09:04.127
THIS GUY WORKS IN DIAMONDS.

09:04.169 --> 09:07.005
HE WANTS TO TALK BUSINESS

09:04.169 --> 09:07.005
OR SOMETHING.

09:07.047 --> 09:09.090
ALL RIGHT.

09:09.132 --> 09:11.510
LAY THE ARMS DOWN, BROTHER.

09:11.551 --> 09:13.261
HE'S COOL.

09:13.303 --> 09:15.347
YOU'LL HAVE TO EXCUSE

09:13.303 --> 09:15.347
MY BODYGUARD.

09:15.389 --> 09:16.890
HE'S TOUCHY.

09:16.931 --> 09:19.851
IT'S 'CAUSE HE'S A MUTE,

09:16.931 --> 09:19.851
ALL RIGHT?

09:19.893 --> 09:23.438
YEAH, WELL, MY BODYGUARDS

09:19.893 --> 09:23.438
DON'T TALK MUCH, EITHER.

09:29.069 --> 09:32.489
WELL, LOOKS LIKE WE FOUND

09:29.069 --> 09:32.489
OUR ARMORED-CAR ROBBERS.

09:39.413 --> 09:41.039
[ GRUNTING ]

09:41.081 --> 09:42.249
[ GUN COCKS ]

09:46.294 --> 09:48.255
GONNA SHOOT

09:46.294 --> 09:48.255
THROUGH YOUR OWN MATE, THEN?

09:48.296 --> 09:51.258
TO BE HONEST WITH YOU,

09:48.296 --> 09:51.258
I NEVER LIKED HIM.

09:52.175 --> 09:55.554
LEGIT.

09:52.175 --> 09:55.554
GOON SQUAD AND ALL, INNIT?

09:55.595 --> 09:57.889
STAND DOWN.

10:04.645 --> 10:06.022
JIM KERRITY.

10:06.064 --> 10:08.942
YOU'RE JIM KERRITY --

10:06.064 --> 10:08.942
KERRITY DIAMONDS?

10:08.983 --> 10:11.152
[ Chuckling ]

10:08.983 --> 10:11.152
OH, NO.

10:11.194 --> 10:13.905
BROTHER, YOU GOT HIT HARD

10:11.194 --> 10:13.905
LAST WEEK.

10:13.947 --> 10:15.949
THE HEIST, YES.

10:13.947 --> 10:15.949
THAT WAS ME.

10:15.990 --> 10:20.328
SO, DID YOU USE THE ROMANOVS

10:15.990 --> 10:20.328
BACK THERE OR JUST HIRE OUT?

10:20.370 --> 10:22.663
I'M IN THE BUSINESS, JIMMY BOY.

10:20.370 --> 10:22.663
I CAN SMELL AN INSIDE JOB.

