DAYS?

14:09.890 --> 14:12.101
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:09.890 --> 14:12.101
MONTHS.

14:12.143 --> 14:13.311
MM. YEAH.

14:13.353 --> 14:15.146
WOW.

14:15.188 --> 14:19.066
WELL...I'LL BE IN TOUCH.

14:19.108 --> 14:20.443
MM-HMM. MM-HMM.

14:22.362 --> 14:25.031
[ DOOR BUZZES ]

14:34.708 --> 14:37.210
I KNOW.

