Parker:

15:38.438 --> 15:39.773
DO NOT INHALE

15:39.814 --> 15:42.483
UNLESS YOU ARE AT LEAST 50 FEET

15:39.814 --> 15:42.483
FROM THE ENTRANCE!

15:42.525 --> 15:45.904
THIS SHOULD ALL BE TAKEN CARE OF

15:42.525 --> 15:45.904
BY TOMORROW, SO NOTHING...

