18:25.271 --> 18:26.606
BUT I'M ONLY HERE

18:25.271 --> 18:26.606
FOR ANOTHER WEEK.

18:26.647 --> 18:28.066
I'VE GOT A THING IN ANTWERP.

18:28.107 --> 18:31.444
ALL RIGHT. WELL, LET'S, UH,

18:28.107 --> 18:31.444
LET'S DO IT TOMORROW?

18:31.485 --> 18:33.071
-DONE.

18:31.485 --> 18:33.071
-EXCELLENT.

18:33.112 --> 18:34.572
MR. ICE.

